# How to reissue SSL?
Here is the steps to re-issue SSL cert for customer:

1) Go to  https://products.geotrust.com/orders/orderinformation/authentication.do
```diagram

```

2)  In that page enter requested details

> Domain name and Email address is enough

3) This will lead you to customer control panel used for specific SSL and the SSL order details will be displayed
```diagram

```

4) Click on Request Access and this will sent an email to the customer with control panel URL 
5) Tell customer to check his email and provide us the URL.
6) Once customer sent the URL, you will able to access control panel and reissue his SSL.
